      "description": "Presenting an immaculate vehicle that serves as a benchmark for its class. This specimen has been preserved in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine example of automotive excellence. Discerning buyers will appreciate the uncompromising integrity and superior presentation of this curated offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
